FBIS4-56365 "drlat085_t_94004" FBIS-LAT-94-085 Daily Report 2 May 1994 Venezuela Homemade Bomb Explodes on Board Caracas Train Homemade Bomb Explodes on Board Caracas Train PA0205132594 Paris AFP in Spanish 1244 GMT 2 May 94 PA0205132594 Paris AFP Spanish BFN [Text] Caracas, 2 May (AFP) -- Police sources have confirmed to AFP a homemade bomb exploded Monday morning on board a Caracas metro train and injured five people. The bomb exploded when the train, packed with commuters going to work, stopped at the Eastern Park Station, in the exclusive area of Los Palos Grandes. The condition of the injured is unknown at this time.
